data.description: Here is your opportunity for home ownership in the Otter Creek Community! Settled in a cul-de-sac, this three-bedroom, two-bathroom home is move-in ready. The spacious family room features a vaulted ceiling and boasts a wood-burning fireplace. You have the option to enjoy meals in the formal dining area, breakfast bar or the breakfast nook nestled next to the bay window. The kitchen is filled with stainless steel appliances and granite countertops. The rear exterior has a freshly painted deck for entertaining or personal comfort. This yard is also fully fenced and ready for family pets. Don't miss out on the abundance of amenities. Enjoy the clubhouse, fitness center, pools, trails and playgrounds - all within minutes of the home!
